msgid ""
"Re-check existing translations using context-aware AI.\n"
"\n"
"Detects entries translated without app name/context\n"
"and fixes only those. Requires an LLM-based API.\n"
"\n"
"Compatible APIs:\n"
"OpenAI, Gemini, Groq, Mistral, OpenRouter, Grok\n"
"\n"
"Not compatible:\n"
"DeepL, LibreTranslate (no context support)"
msgstr ""
"Kontrollera befintliga översättningar igen med kontextmedveten AI.\n"
"\n"
"Upptäcker poster översatta utan appnamn/kontext\n"
"och korrigerar endast dessa. Kräver ett LLM-baserat API.\n"
"\n"
"Kompatibla API:er:\n"
"OpenAI, Gemini, Groq, Mistral, OpenRouter, Grok\n"
"\n"
"Ej kompatibla:\n"
"DeepL, LibreTranslate (inget kontextstöd)"
